Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're going\Nto the Appleoosa County Fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal shows,\Ncarnival rides...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And all kinds of\Nfood on a stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of food, did you\Npack snacks for the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For there AND back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And our train\Ntickets are all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've got our whole\Nitinerary planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're\Nnot {\i1}Twilight's{\i0} sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Weeks of planning has\Nall come down to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do now is wait\Nfor our chaperone to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [musical clock ticking] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So when's Rainbow\NDash coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were\Ngonna ask Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose\Nyou asked Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we spent all\Nthis time planning a trip
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and none of us asked\Nanypony to take us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In our defense, every\N{\i1}other{\i0} part of the trip
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,was planned really well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We really did think\Nof everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,except finding\Nsomepony to take us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fair is\Nonly today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, darlings, but I\Ncan't possibly go to Appleoosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised to deliver a new\Ndesign to Fancy Pants for his
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Monocle and Top Hat\NAppreciation Society Soiree.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you finish\Nit tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I could, but you'll\Nlearn as you get older
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,how important it is to\Nkeep your promises,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,especially when\Nrunning a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should just\Ngo by ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT? Oh, my dear, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Appleoosa is far too long a\Ntrain ride for young foals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,without accompaniment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You could end up in the\Nwrong place entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you see if\NRainbow Dash is free?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I just heard from\NSpitfire that a whole bunch of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,storm clouds got loose\Nfrom the cloud factory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and she needs every\NWonderbolt to help bust 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on Rainbow Dash,\Nthey won't miss ONE pony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and we really want\Nto go to the fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, we're too\Nyoung to go alone..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Young ponies like\Nyou could get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and never find\Nyour way back,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a Wonderbolt isn't\N{\i1}just{\i0} about showing off,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it's also a\Nresponsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand\Nwhen you get older.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll find\Nsomepony else to take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could, sugarcube.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Big Mac's not\Nfeeling well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But Big Mac's old enough\Nto take care of {\i1}himself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd all have so\Nmuch fun together..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes taking\Ncare of somepony
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is more important\Nthan having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, don't\Nyou even THINK about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to go without a grown\Npony there to take care of YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You could end up in\Nhot water, or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The fair could be over before\Nwe find somepony to take us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But then we thought of YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the fair will\Nbe full of all sorts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of animals and creatures....!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but Twilight\Nhas an important
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,magical research project and\Nshe's asked for my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that means\NTwilight's busy too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I am. Starswirl\Nsent me this enchanted flower
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and it isn't doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I figure out its\Nmagical properties,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we can save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's a "no" on going\Nwith us to the fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already asked\NApplejack, Rainbow Dash,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rarity and none\Nof them can come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And everypony\Nmade it clear
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we're too young\Nto go on our own...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You could take the wrong\Ntrain or miss your stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or get lost in a\Nstrange town and end up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in a dangerous situation\Nwith nopony to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard,\Nbut sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you just can't do\Nwhat you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure if YOU wanted\Nto go to the fair you could...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, grownups can do a lot\Nof things that foals can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's plenty\Nwe can't do either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Like right now, I can't\Nfind a SINGLE reference
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to this flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the birds or\Ninsects I've talked to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,have heard of it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's anything\Nin Shadetail Evergreen's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tome of Flora and Fauna?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That book's {\i1}pretty{\i0}\Nout of date,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but it might be\Nworth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a copy in\Nthe library filed under
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Discontinued But Still\NPotentially Useful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ancient Texts."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless I put it under\N"Hokum With A Slight Chance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of Practical Applications."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this flower is\Nthe most interesting thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we're gonna see today..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you count watching\NTwilight struggle to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,how she organizes her books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet every pony in Equestria\Nis in Appleoosa right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Every pony but US.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we didn't have\Nto wait to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it would\Nhappen all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'd know everything\Nwe'd need to get to the fair
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and back with no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish we were\Nas old as our sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then nopony could\Ntell us what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd be able to\Ntake care of ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [chimes] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sweetie Belle, why's\Nyour face all lit up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,WE CAN GO TO THE FAIR!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you brought\Nthe tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta hurry if we're\Ngoing to make the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out how\Nfast we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Grownup legs are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much of\Nthis my scooter can take!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And nopony yelled at us\Nto slow down even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Being a grownup is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're grownup ponies\Nnow. We can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And all those worries\NTwilight and the others had
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,don't apply anymore\Nbecause we're big!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And being big is all it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Woke up this morning{\i0}\N{\i1} feeling tired and small ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But look at us now! We{\i0}\N{\i1} must be ninety feet tall. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Don't have to worry{\i0}\N{\i1} 'bout making mistakes ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ because being big{\i0}\N{\i1} is all it takes! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ A tiny twist of fate{\i0}\N{\i1} brought on this big change. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Give me room, gotta zoom! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I've got plans to arrange ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can do what I want, be{\i0}\N{\i1} it run, trot, or traipse, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ 'cause being big{\i0}\N{\i1} is all it takes. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Being big isn't{\i0}\N{\i1} just a size. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ At bedtime we don't even{\i0}\N{\i1} have to close our eyes. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're in control now,{\i0}\N{\i1} for goodness sake ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ 'cause being big{\i0}\N{\i1} is all it takes! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Leaving behind the{\i0}\N{\i1} little pony you've known, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ steppin' out, growin' up,{\i0}\N{\i1} makin' moves of my own. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You can't tell me no. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ There's no place I can't go: ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ mountains, cities,{\i0}\N{\i1} jungles, or lakes, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ 'cause being big{\i0}\N{\i1} is all it takes. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Being big isn't just a size ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We'll tell you our opinion{\i0}\N{\i1} 'cause we're oh so wise ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're in control now,{\i0}\N{\i1} for goodness sake ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ 'cause being big{\i0}\N{\i1} is all it takes! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I can eat all the snacks cause{\i0}\N{\i1} that's for me to decide. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We know how it all works,{\i0}\N{\i1} even what we ain't tried! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Facts don't matter now{\i0}\N{\i1} cause it's not what we know ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We can win any{\i0}\N{\i1} argument with ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ "Because I say so!" ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can't stop us now, don't{\i0}\N{\i1} try to stand in our way! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're awake, gonna take ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ All we can from today ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Once we had to listen now{\i0}\N{\i1} you'll hear what we say ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Everything is always OK! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Cause being big is all{\i0}\N{\i1} it takes! All it takes! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I ate\Ntoo many snacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, this doesn't\Nlook like Appleoosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[nasty gravelly voice]\NThat's because it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [eerie music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You all heard that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Hello? Do you think\Nwe got on the wrong train?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought trains just took\Nyou where you wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I don't mean to laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but you three must\Nnot travel much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hayseed Junction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The train to Appleoosa\Nisn't for a few hours..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, you could\Nset off on {\i1}hoof{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's treacherous\N{\i1}and{\i0} confusing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,unfit for the\Nyoung or timid..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But you three are\Ngrownups. You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write down\Nsome directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should\Nwait for the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And miss the fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We already ended up\Nin the wrong place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which is exactly what\Nwe were warned about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And.. what if we can't\Nfollow the directions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! We didn't come\Nall this way for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've been through\Na swamp as a young pony,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,as a grownup, it'll be a snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Grownups {\i1}always{\i0}\Nknow the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because being big\Nis all it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I've got kind\Nof a throat thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [rhythmic piano] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! [splash]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, are you\Nsure this is the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [scary music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't DO that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom: Girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should head\Nback to the station..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure we can.\NI think we're lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Twilight\Nand the others said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, where were you when I was\Nfeeding and caring for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,AHHH! Wild swamp ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not wild swamp ponies,\Nwe're just grownups!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are\N{\i1}definitely{\i0} NOT lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. But that swamp\Nis pretty confusing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're not from\Naround here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Spur and this is Biscuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Apple Bloom, nice to meet\Nyou, but.. we're not {\i1}confused{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just... exploring\Nnew ways to Appleoosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's where\Nwe're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Biscuit thinks he can\Njust take Bloofy, here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? It's just up the\Nroad and Bloofy's MY pet too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when? Bloofy's\Nnever even seen a CROWD,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which you'd know if you\Never took care of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever think\Nmeeting all those ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,might be good for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems OK meeting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See? They're grownups\Nand THEY get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloofy should totally come\Nto the fair with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all don't really\Nthink that, do ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Hold on, us\Ngrownups need to confer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you girls think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If they go to the\Nfair, we can tag along!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And Spur probably\N{\i1}should{\i0} share Bloofy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's something a\Ngrownup would say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As grownup ponies, we think\Nyou should SHARE Bloofy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and let Biscuit take\Nhim to the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That is some quality\Ngrownup advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But Bloofy's never been around\Nanything that exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What if something\Ngoes wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're headed to\Nthe fair too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're such\Ngreat advice givers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,feel free to ask\Nus for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ho ho! It's everything\NI thought it'd be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my goodness, what\Nan interesting critter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You should enter him\Nin the animal showcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be sure to win most\Ninteresting creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Animals showcase? That's\Nexactly what we should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems like a bad idea.\NWhat do you grownups think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [upbeat music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to being\Nable to ask your advice!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You ran off the\Nsecond we got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Biscuit\Nand Bloofy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came\Nto find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [fanfare] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Spur: It's one thing to\Nbring Bloofy to the fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's another to\Nstick him in a showcase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed\Nto be sharing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm with Biscuit. The\Nshowcase looks like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if I think\Ntaking care of Bloofy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is more important\Nthan having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloofy's just excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably just\Nwants to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [delicate music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're not just\Nupset you have to share him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you took\Na little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, like, {\i1}leave{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If sharing him is too hard,\Nthat might be the best thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take our word for\Nit. We are grownups..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\NSpur's so worried about;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloofy and Biscuit\Nare having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What could\Ngo wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [dramatic music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and my big grownup mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [tense music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this\Nqualifies as getting into
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a dangerous situation with\Nno grown pony to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think WE'RE the grown ponies\Nthat need to be helping today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,BLOOFY! TREATS, TREATS,\NTREATS! Who wants a treat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,RUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're right about\Nthe girls coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, once we read Shadetail\NEvergreen's warning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that the flower grants\Nwishes, it wasn't a stretch
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to think they wished\Nthemselves to the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all they were\Ntalking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe since we told them\Nthey were too young to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,they wished to become\Ngrownups, then came here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and caused some\Nkind of trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that led to a\Ntown-wide panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Or that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Fluttershy!\NOh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're not\Ngonna believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's me, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Scootaloo! We kinda\Ngot turned into grownups!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And we thought we could\Ntake the train here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,since we were old enough, but\Nwe ended up in the wrong place,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,just like you said we would!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you said we would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we met these foals\Nwho led us to the fair
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and we tried to give them\Nsome grownup-style advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but it turned their\Npet into a tornado
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that might destroy\Nthe whole town!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! A Whirling Mungtooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They are very rare, and just\Nthe cutest little things
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when they're not excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo: How do we calm him down!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When they're young, a\NMungtooth forms a tight bond
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,with its caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the only ones who can\Nget them to stop spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spur's the one who really\Ntook care of Bloofy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You all go look\Nfor Spur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy and I\Nwill do our best
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep everypony\Nhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT'S Bloofy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Spur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew what was best\Nfor him all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though we\Nseem like grownups,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you were way more\Nresponsible than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean\N"seem" like grownups?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we don't have\Ntime to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we have\Nto stop this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're the only\None who can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you. He mostly\Njust needs to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there Bloofy-boo.\NIt's OK..!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know\Nwhat to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After years of\Nexperience with animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've picked up\Na few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one thing's\Nfor sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloofy definitely earned
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the most interesting\Ncreature prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I didn't\Nlisten to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess grownups\Naren't always perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure aren't.\NBut young foals
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending to be grownups\Nare even less so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one petal left,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think the three of\Nyou know what to wish for
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm pretty sure\NStarswirl won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We wish we were foals again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. You three are\Nactually younger than us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower turned\Nus into grownups,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so we figured we could\Ndo whatever we wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess that's\Nnot exactly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We did everything real\Ngrownups told us not to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and caused all\Nkinds of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And things could have\Nbeen a lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we {\i1}were{\i0}\Npretty selfish...
